"n.综合，合成 【英】 n. 综合，合成(the combining of separate things, ideas into a complete whole) 【考】 反义词：analysis(分 解) n. 综合, 合成(把分别的元素或物质连接成连贯的一个整体) 【记】syn = same, thes放, is: 把同样的东西放在一起－综合 【参】antithetic(adj 正相反的; 对立的)anti反, thet放, ic 【反】analysis(n 分析; 分解); take apart(分解) 【记】syn + thesis 论文， 多篇论文放到一起，综合而成 synthesis (n.)  1610s, ""deductive reasoning,"" from Latin synthesis ""collection, set, suit of clothes, composition (of a medication),"" from Greek synthesis ""composition, a putting together,"" from syntithenai ""put together, combine,"" from syn- ""together"" (see syn-) + tithenai ""put, place"" (see theme). From 1733 as ""a combination of parts into a whole."" Earlier borrowed in Middle English as sintecis (mid-15c.). Plural syntheses."
